153
00:08:47,876 --> 00:08:50,293
Really interesting object,
you have Enceladus,

154
00:08:50,294 --> 00:08:54,166
which is similar
in its structure to Europa,

155
00:08:54,167 --> 00:08:58,041
which we talked about before,
covered with solid ice,

156
00:08:58,042 --> 00:09:03,584
